  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-about-hero">
    <h1 class="section-heading" id="section-about-hero">About Us</h1>

    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="about-lede">We are a Bangalore-based community-theatre troupe. We make up theatre on the spot, with no script and no second take, and we would like to rekindle the joy of being playful and whimsical.</p>
      <p class="about-where">Improv Lore has been around since 2022. When Underline Center opened in Indiranagar, we made it our home, and we have been the resident improv act there ever since. Our Wednesday jam is the longest-running night the venue has. We also play other rooms around the city, and now and then we take a show out of town.</p>
      <p class="more-line">Out of town has lately meant out of the country. Since 2024 we have been invited to improv festivals across Asia, in Singapore, Vietnam, Manila, and Hong Kong. <a href="/festivals/">See where we've played →</a></p>
    </div>

